CommandInformation.​s_counter

Counter of command types

Fields
v

Count of geometric vertices

vn

Count of vertex normals

vt

Count of texture vertices

vp

Count of parameter space vertices

f

Count of faces

l

Count of lines

p

Count of points

shapes

Shapes
